PrecisApproval that CANADA MORTGAGE AND HOUSING CORPORATION pay to the Receiver General for Canada as revenues of Canada, an amount originating from the former Home Improvement Loan Insurance Fund established under the National Housing Act, being an amount considered to be in excess of the amount required for the purposes of the Corporation.
